Package org.shogun

Class NativeLibraryLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.shogun.NativeLibraryLoader

  • public class NativeLibraryLoader
extends java.lang.Object
    Java Class to manage native libraries. We load the main jar which is defined as root node in the lddtree.txt file. Optionally we can install the folder with all binaries in the temp directory and load the binaries from there. We support complex library scenarios by interpreting the dependency hierarchy which is provided by lddtree.
    Author:
    pschatzmann
